# 詞：睇怕

1. 睇怕今日會落大雨，你帶把傘先好。 (It looks like it's going to rain heavily today; you'd better bring an umbrella.)
2. 睇怕佢今日唔會嚟開會，因為佢電話都打唔通。 (It seems he won't come to the meeting today because we can't reach him by phone.)
3. 睇怕呢單生意好難做成，因為對方要求太高。 (It looks like this deal is hard to close because the other party's demands are too high.)
4. 睇怕佢好鍾意你呢個朋友，成日問起你哋嘅事。 (It seems he really likes your friend; he always asks about you two.)
5. 睇怕個電影唔係咁好笑，好多人都中途離場。 (It looks like the movie wasn't that funny; many people left halfway through.)
6. 睇怕佢最近壓力好大，成日都見佢好攰。 (It appears he's under a lot of stress recently; he always looks very tired.)
7. 睇怕佢唔係故意遲到，可能係路上塞車。 (It seems he didn't mean to be late; maybe he was stuck in traffic.)
8. 睇怕呢間餐廳嘅菜式好正，好多人都排隊。 (It looks like this restaurant's dishes are great; many people are queuing up.)
9. 睇怕佢好緊張，手都抖緊。 (It seems he's very nervous; his hands are shaking.)
10. 睇怕佢唔係真心想幫你，只係講講笑咋。 (It looks like he doesn't really want to help you; he's just joking.) [end of text]


